title: How to Stop Other People from Winning Roblox Tycoons

steps.headline: Login and head to the catalog.
steps.description: The catalog is located on the bar on top of the screen, right after games.

steps.headline: Click on gear.
steps.description: Search paintball and click a paintball gun that you like. Don't click red though, most tycoons have red buttons.

steps.headline: Enter a tycoon with gear allowed and get a tycoon.
Enter another person’s tycoon if possible.
steps.description: If this is not possible, then repeat steps 1 to 3 until you've found one.

steps.headline: Use the paintball gun on buttons.
Leave tycoon or upgrade income to build more stuff quicker.

text: Login and head to the catalog. The catalog is located on the bar on top of the screen, right after games. Click on gear. Search paintball and click a paintball gun that you like. Don't click red though, most tycoons have red buttons. Enter a tycoon with gear allowed and get a tycoon.  Enter another person’s tycoon if possible. If this is not possible, then repeat steps 1 to 3 until you've found one. Use the paintball gun on buttons.  Leave tycoon or upgrade income to build more stuff quicker.
